metaphor: I'll Only Take the Long Way if You Pay Me
scene_description: the background is composed of black pixels. there is a shape made with grey lines that are 1 pixel wide. inside of the grey shape there is a single blue pixel and a single yellow pixel.
literal_instruction: remove the yellow pixel and the blue pixel. to do this, replace each of them with a black pixel. in the 1st row from the top, place a single blue pixel in the 6th column from the right.
